6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to tax; creating the Oklahoma Tax
Laundering Prevention Act of 2026; providing for
8 noncodification; and providing for an effective date.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
13 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
14 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma Tax
15 Laundering Prevention Act of 2026".
16 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
